Package Main.Models

Class GodModePowerUp

java.lang.Object
Main.Models.GodModePowerUp
public class GodModePowerUp
extends java.lang.Object
Public class GodModePowerUp is used to create a power up for the game with the given center point and diameter. It holds all the relevant information about the power up such as colour, position and spawn and collected flags so that the power up can be rendered in the game. All the setters and getters required are also here.
Since:
28/11/2021
Version:

Author:
